language Essence 1.3

given w: int(1..)
given g: int(1..)
given s: int(1..)
letting nGolfers be g * s
letting Golfers be new type of size nGolfers
find sched: matrix indexed by [int(1..w)] of function (total) Golfers --> int(1..g)
such that and([and([sum([toInt(image(sched[i], p) = j) | p : Golfers]) = s | j : int(1..g)]) | i : int(1..w)])
such that
    and([and([p1 != p2 -> sum([toInt(image(sched[i], p1) = image(sched[i], p2)) | i : int(1..w)]) <= 1 | p2 : Golfers])
             | p1 : Golfers])

